info.name: Finobe Home Background Size Fix
info.description: This style for Finobe will fix the sizing issue for the backgrounds on Finobe's new home page! (Style by connor on finobe)

style.css: @keyframes  janky{0%{background:url(img/homeback.jpg) no-repeat center center fixed;background-size: cover;}50%{background:url(img/homeback.jpg) no-repeat center center fixed;background-size: cover;}100%{background:url(img/dark.jpg) no-repeat center center fixed;background-size: cover;}}
